{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"63922de4e2","title":"给杨开英的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"76ad688af5","index":0,"year":1956,"month":12,"day":16,"articleId":"63922de4e2"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"152d99e2f7","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"63922de4e2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"杨开英，毛泽东夫人杨开慧的堂妹。当时任大连第三中学副教导主任。毛世美，现名毛臻，毛泽东的远房径孙。"},{"id":"2ef465ba45","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"63922de4e2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指杨开智和杨开慧的母亲向振熙。即杨开慧之兄杨开智（字子珍）和他的夫人李崇德。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4f36ab7173","type":"title","text":"给杨开英“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"63922de4e2"},{"id":"152d99e2f7","type":"paragraph","text":"开英同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"63922de4e2"},{"id":"2ef465ba45","type":"paragraph","text":"很久以前接你一信，甚为高兴。拖延未复，以后查不到你的地址了。近日毛世美他们来看我，知道你在大连的育英中学做教务长，又说你仍患肺病，甚为系念。寄上一点钱以供医药之用。如有所需，尚望告我。我的情况尚好。杨老太太以及杨子珍天妇“和我便有联系。便时望以你的情况见告。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"63922de4e2"},{"id":"12f1e647be","type":"paragraph","text":"祝好！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"63922de4e2"},{"id":"939cd89889","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"63922de4e2"},{"id":"0aba66ac81","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年十二月十六日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"63922de4e2"}],"page":{"id":"1385489d66","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"63922de4e2","start":193,"end":193}}}},"__N_SSG":true}